== 製作 ==
2013年11月11日，[[伊卓瑞斯·艾巴|伊卓瑞斯·艾巴]]加入電影劇組<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2013/film/news/idris-elba-bastille-day-1200819619/|title=Idris Elba Set to Star in Thriller ‘Bastille Day’ (EXCLUSIVE)|work=Variety|accessdate=4 December 2014|archive-date=2016-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160422084439/http://variety.com/2013/film/news/idris-elba-bastille-day-1200819619/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年5月18日，[[焦點影業|焦點影業]]買下了本片在美國的發行權<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/118464-focus-features-acquires-bastille-day-starring-idris-elba|title=Focus Features Acquires Bastille Day, Starring Idris Elba|work=ComingSoon.net|accessdate=4 December 2014|archive-date=2016-08-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160810195236/http://www.comingsoon.net/movies/news/118464-focus-features-acquires-bastille-day-starring-idris-elba|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年10月2日，宣布[[理察·麥登|理察·麥登]]參演了本片<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/richard-madden-bastille-day-casting-1201319740/|title=‘Game of Thrones’ Star Richard Madden Joins Idris Elba in ‘Bastille Day’ (EXCLUSIVE)|work=Variety|accessdate=4 December 2014|archive-date=2020-11-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201111231529/https://variety.com/2014/film/news/richard-madden-bastille-day-casting-1201319740/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影正式於2014年10月13日在[[巴黎|巴黎]]開拍，直到2014年12月17日[[殺青|殺青]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2014/film/news/idris-elbas-bastille-day-goes-into-production-in-paris-1201334618/|title=Idris Elba’s ‘Bastille Day’ Goes Into Production in Paris|work=Variety|accessdate=4 December 2014|archive-date=2020-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201202095931/https://variety.com/2014/film/news/idris-elbas-bastille-day-goes-into-production-in-paris-1201334618/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ssninsider.com/on-the-set-for-121914-emilia-clarke-wraps-voice-from-the-stone-idris-elba-finishes-up-bastille-day-more/ |title=On the Set for 12/19/14: Emilia Clarke Wraps Voice from the Stone, Idris Elba Finishes Up Bastille Day & More |publisher=Ssninsider.com |date= |accessdate=2015-04-10 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304052333/http://www.ssninsider.com/on-the-set-for-121914-emilia-clarke-wraps-voice-from-the-stone-idris-elba-finishes-up-bastille-day-more/ |archivedate=2016-03-04 }}</ref>。

== 發行 ==
電影原定2016年2月19日在英國上映，但因[[2015年11月巴黎襲擊事件|2015年11月巴黎襲擊事件]]的緣故而延遲<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2015/film/news/paris-attacks-bastille-day-release-idris-elba-taj-mahal-1201643581/|title=Studiocanal Rethinks Idris Elba’s ‘Bastille Day’ Release, Bac Proceeds With ‘Taj Mahal’ Bow|last=Keslassy|first=Elsa|date=18 November 2015|accessdate=24 July 2016|work=Variety|archive-date=2020-12-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201204214441/https://variety.com/2015/film/news/paris-attacks-bastille-day-release-idris-elba-taj-mahal-1201643581/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影於2016年4月22日同時在英國、愛爾蘭和瑞典上映，而法國則定於2016年7月13日推出。繼[[2016年尼斯襲擊事件|2016年尼斯襲擊事件]]後，[[通道影業|通道影業]]為了給予受害者和家屬尊重，於2016年7月17日從戲院撤下了電影<ref name=lemonade>{{cite web|url=http://www.lemonde.fr/cinema/article/2016/07/17/le-film-d-action-bastille-day-deprogramme-apres-l-attentat-de-nice_4970742_3476.html|title=''Le film d’action « Bastille Day » déprogrammé après l’attentat de Nice''|language=fr|publisher=Le Monde|date=17 July 2016|accessdate=24 July 2016|archive-date=2020-11-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201130182818/https://www.lemonde.fr/cinema/article/2016/07/17/le-film-d-action-bastille-day-deprogramme-apres-l-attentat-de-nice_4970742_3476.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2016/07/nice-attack-bastille-day-film-studiocanal-1201787671/|title=Studiocanal Requests Idris Elba Action Pic ‘Bastille Day’ Be Pulled From French Theaters|last=Lincoln|first=Ross|date=16 July 2016|accessdate=24 July 2016|archive-date=2020-11-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201127095109/https://deadline.com/2016/07/nice-attack-bastille-day-film-studiocanal-1201787671/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

